{"tid":2266873,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"男醫生要求性愛還債    女護士殺人烹屍被判死刑","createTime":"2020-11-01T15:49:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-02T16:21:58.000Z","uid":112551,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c0e065390626158b8e58811b7189ecaf2a1082a2","tid":2266873,"uid":112551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T15:49:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/5qQnkskvjXiXdS.W06Va.w--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-11/b41a9eb0-1c10-11eb-bc2b-5fef8118facd\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F5qQnkskvjXiXdS.W06Va.w--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-11%2Fb41a9eb0-1c10-11eb-bc2b-5fef8118facd&h=2c0771c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n廣西壯族自治區玉林市中級人民法院在周五（30日），對日前轟動一時的護士殺人烹屍案作出宣判。25歲女護士李鳳萍因故意殺人罪被判死刑；盜竊罪則被判有期徒刑5年，罰款3萬元（人民幣，下同，約3.5萬港元），數罪併罰。法院決定執行死刑，剝奪其政治權利終身；同時，法院責令被告向受害人羅遠健的親屬賠償9.8萬元（約11.52萬港元）。<br />\n<br />\n事發於今年3月23日，被告在租住單位內殺害同院50歲骨科醫生羅遠健，將其碎屍烹煮。另外，更將煮熟的屍塊沖下溝渠。李女事後憶述，指自己沉迷賭博，欠下債務，曾向羅男借錢5萬元（約5.8萬港元）還債，事後被對方要求每周與他發生性行為3次，且不准她找男朋友，亦不可接觸其他男人。<br />\n<br />\n李女事後再因賭欠債20萬（約23.51萬港元），只好再問羅男借錢，羅男答應後要求李女簽下30萬（約35.2萬港元）的借據，並要求她「隨傳隨到」，滿足自己的性需要。李女接受條件後，邀請對方到寓所喝酒並發生關係。但李女心有不甘，趁對方酒後熟睡，將其殺害，再盜走他的財物。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />前後借咗30萬，簽咗仲心有不甘，唔還仲要殺人。"},{"pid":"0f04fff75a6cc1fd2a9ff4ae68653a39512eaa11","tid":2266873,"uid":49336,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T15:51:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f036a4af84dbf429f20acdb5a5de008d4e254d6a","tid":2266873,"uid":25316,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T15:52:12.000Z","msg":"咁撚豬都肯俾你用性愛還債仲想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fad2f4b3947cc34cd1440b8269b0f39023e94f35","tid":2266873,"uid":110832,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T15:57:40.000Z","msg":"賤女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6c48f03146de3bd42543e2431b61ba0b5590feb","tid":2266873,"uid":112551,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T16:10:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c7d2b97e0b6f228f28afdd524c33cfd94aa90b7","tid":2266873,"uid":226955,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T16:14:43.000Z","msg":"比人（強姦 / 雞姦）一次可以等同還30萬債務，究竟連登仔肯唔肯呢？<br />\n<br />\n肯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔肯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"699aabd59588bed28380f2e1ae404ba2f85163ff","tid":2266873,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T16:16:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ba51ca380a93d08b7798dc7970ab824d56993bec","tid":2266873,"uid":121580,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0f04fff75a6cc1fd2a9ff4ae68653a39512eaa11","tid":2266873,"uid":49336,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T15:51:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T16:18:03.000Z","msg":"小學雞?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nm=萬?"},{"pid":"d10e713d2f205cc54a8265b827f3404934d2b61b","tid":2266873,"uid":137160,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T16:20:33.000Z","msg":"😦😦"},{"pid":"8021eff37e606c952b505438392d476e381cc2f3","tid":2266873,"uid":275114,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9c7d2b97e0b6f228f28afdd524c33cfd94aa90b7","tid":2266873,"uid":226955,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T16:14:43.000Z","msg":"比人（強姦 / 雞姦）一次可以等同還30萬債務，究竟連登仔肯唔肯呢？<br />\n<br />\n肯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔肯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" c